OL,3,C'Severe disruption' expected with bus
OL,4,Cstrikes: What you need to know
OL,6,F"Severe disruption" is expected across
OL,7,Fa travel network as more than 2,000
OL,8,Fbus workers are set to strike over low
OL,9,Fpay.
OL,11,FStaff from Greater Manchester's Bee
OL,12,FNetwork are set to strike from Friday
OL,13,F19 September to Monday 22 September,
OL,14,Fwith another strike now announced for
OL,15,F30 September-2 October.
OL,17,FThe Unite union said the strikes
OL,18,Finvolve staff at Stagecoach, First Bus
OL,19,FRochdale and Metroline, with around
OL,20,Ftwo thirds of buses in Greater
OL,21,FManchester expected to not run.
