OL,3,C'Severe disruption' expected with bus
OL,4,Cstrikes: What you need to know
OL,6,FIn response, Transport for Greater
OL,7,FManchester (TGFM) says passengers will
OL,8,Fstill be able to travel on most trains
OL,9,Fin affected areas, and additional
OL,10,Ftrams with extra capacity will be
OL,11,Favailable where possible.
OL,13,FA TGFM spokesperson said: "There are
OL,14,Falternatives for people, but
OL,15,Funfortunately there aren't
OL,16,Falternatives for everybody, so we are
OL,17,Fencouraging people to check on the
OL,18,Fwebsite which will say what is and
OL,19,Fisn't running."
