OL,3,C'Severe disruption' expected with bus
OL,4,Cstrikes: What you need to know
OL,6,F"They've come to Manchester to get a
OL,7,Ffoot hold in the game, to get involved
OL,8,Fin the franchising and what they've
OL,9,Ffailed to do is budget accordingly for
OL,10,Fpay rises for the staff."
OL,12,FPaul Townley, General Manager of First
OL,13,FBus in Rochdale, said: "We are
OL,14,Fdisappointed not to have reached a
OL,15,Ffinal agreement and that strike action
OL,16,Fwill go ahead from tomorrow (Friday 19
OL,17,FSeptember) up to and including Monday
OL,18,F22 September.
