OL,3,C'Severe disruption' expected with bus
OL,4,Cstrikes: What you need to know
OL,6,F"Constructive talks have been held
OL,7,Fwith Unite and we hope to reach a
OL,8,Fresolution as soon as possible. The
OL,9,Fmanagement team at First Bus in
OL,10,FRochdale continues to work hard to
OL,11,Ffind solutions to help our valued
OL,12,Fdrivers during these tough economic
OL,13,Ftimes.
OL,15,F"Customers are advised to check the
OL,16,FBee Network website and its social
OL,17,Fmedia for the latest information on
OL,18,Fservices affected.
