OL,3,C'Severe disruption' expected with bus
OL,4,Cstrikes: What you need to know
OL,6,F"We wish to avoid any further
OL,7,FIndustrial action. This is not the way
OL,8,Fforward and will be damaging to
OL,9,Feveryone, causing severe disruption to
OL,10,Fthe daily lives of our customers who
OL,11,Frely on the bus to get to work,
OL,12,Feducation and for appointments."
OL,14,FMembers rejected a pay offer in August
OL,15,Fthis year, with more strikes now
OL,16,Fplanned for the end of September.
