OL,3,C'Severe disruption' expected with bus
OL,4,Cstrikes: What you need to know
OL,6,FA Metroline Manchester spokesperson
OL,7,Fsaid: "We are extremely disappointed
OL,8,Fin Unite's decision to announce strike
OL,9,Faction. We value our drivers and have
OL,10,Fcontinuously engaged with Unite to
OL,11,Fwork for a positive outcome.
OL,13,F"Our improved offer of an 8.8%
OL,14,Fincrease over two years significantly
OL,15,Fexceeds inflation and would ensure
OL,16,Fthat our drivers continue be amongst
OL,17,Fthe best paid outside of London.
